<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Visiting information</h3>
<p>Whatever your reason for coming into Stepping Hill Hospital, ensuring our patients receive the best possible care, with understanding and compassion, is our highest priority. We realise that putting your health in someone else's hands can sometimes be a daunting experience.<br/><br/>We also understand that coming into hospital is often an unfamiliar experience so the information found in this part of our website we hope will give you the answers to some of your questions and will help you prepare for admission and give you an idea of what to expect when you arrive - see www.stockport.nhs.uk</p>
